ActStandards Council of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of W.A. SAM SHAW of Edmonton, Alberta, to be a member of the Standards Council of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and designation of W.A. SAM SHAW as Vice-Chairperson of the Standards Council of Canada.
